author: National Geographic
description:
A queen bee's pheromone helps her workers locate and protect her—it's this chemical reaction that makes the historical art of bee bearding possible.
Watch David Blaine try this classic act in David Blaine: Do Not Attempt, Sundays at 9/8c on National Geographic. Stream episodes one and two on Disney+ and Hulu.
title: @DavidBlaine learns the art of bee bearing #DavidBlaineDoNotAttempt

description:
